title: #92Noon Friday Football Feast Live From BWW in Champlin
description: Chad Greenway joins Nordo and Charch live from Buffalo Wild Wings in Champlin, where the boys rehash the nightmare that was last night's game. Which players made the grade? Exhausted from calling last night's game, a very tired PA joins mid feast. Comparing injuries sustained jumping off the Vikings bandwagon and Everson Griffin's statement.
